  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>The Level 3 NCFE Diploma in Specialist Support for Teaching &amp; Learning in Schools is for anyone wanting to work in a school or college environment, supporting students and class teachers.</p>]]></mainContent>
